<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="famous-adj">famous <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'feɪməs/    美 /'feɪməs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-well-known">1.★ <strong>著名的；出名的 (well-known)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is better to be faithful than famous.
守信誉胜过有名气。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He is <strong>famous as</strong> a writer. 
他是一位著名的作家。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Zhejiang is <strong>famous for</strong> tea and silk.
浙江以茶叶和丝绸而闻名。</p></div></div>